## Quick Start

### 1. Configure credentials

```bash
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your credentials
```

### 2. Start services

```bash
docker compose up -d
```

### 3. View dashboards

Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) for the Evidence dashboard.
{% if sl_type == 'cube_oss' %}
Cube Playground is at [http://localhost:4000](http://localhost:4000).
{% endif %}

